    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Water drawn through taps from pipes in a dwelling or other structure. Due to its noncorrosive properties, tap water may be used in conservation of ancient stone materials in preference to distilled water.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
